data.description: Motivated Seller! You won't want to miss this very well maintained 4 bed, 2 bath home located in a great neighborhood in Goshen.  Don't let the photos fool you, this home is larger than it appears! The spacious family room offers a great space for entertaining and relaxing. Outside is a nice sized yard, composite deck, firepit, and a shed for additional storage.  The heated garage makes working on your car comfortable during the Indiana winters.  The finished basement allows extra space to spread out, work out, or entertain in.  This home is in great condition and move in ready.  All appliances are included and seller is willing to leave some furniture to make moving day even easier!
